{
  "texts": [
    "To address data scarcity in deep learning, Alzubaidi et al. (2023) have conducted a survey where they provided various solutions and tips to solve the challenge of data scarcity.",
    "One such solution is transfer learning, where pre-trained models on related tasks are fine-tuned with limited data.",
    "Shamrat et al. (2023), AlSaeed and Omar (2022), Tufail et al. (2022), Balboni et al. (2022), Ghazal and Issa (2022) etc.",
    "have incorporated TL to tackle data scarcity.",
    "Moreover, Zhao et al. (2020), Roychowdhury and Roychowdhury (2020), Chui et al. (2022) and Jung et al. (2023), used generative adversarial networks for synthetic data generation."
  ]
}